description: Kallebäck Property Invest AB engages in the real estate business. The company is headquartered in Vasteras, Vastmanland and currently employs 0 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-03-28. The firm operates as a real estate company that purchases, develops, manages and lets real estate or companies that own real estate, obtain financing for its business and conduct business related thereto. The firm operates Naringsfastigheter Kalleback AB as a wholly owned subsidiary.
